    "name": "神奇动物养殖中心：放置好时光",
    "steam_appid": 3064030,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这是一款温馨放松的收集类游戏，各种神奇动物会在你屏幕的下方生活，无论你是在工作、学习，还是悠闲地看视频，它都会陪伴你度过每一天。在这充满魅力的奇幻世界，隐藏有神秘的未知动物。捕捉并创造新的神奇物种，发挥你的创造力，培育出独属于你的神奇动物世界。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3064030/extras/8f652bbe6018103df8dc477d48f64dcd.avif?t=1768882111\" width=616 height=72 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >踏上这场奇妙旅程，解锁各种充满秘密和惊喜的生物群落。阳光草原、恐怖幽林、黄金沙滩...每个新区域都藏着稀有的神秘小动物，等待你的发现！快来捕捉它们，或通过融合创造出独一无二的新物种吧。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3064030/extras/a88156365140aab6de71298ee438cb9c.poster.avif?t=1768882111\" width=616 height=324 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3064030/extras/a88156365140aab6de71298ee438cb9c.webm?t=1768882111\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3064030/extras/a88156365140aab6de71298ee438cb9c.mp4?t=1768882111\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3064030/extras/55d98d6427dfd0cd68173a64e48390a3.avif?t=1768882111\" width=616 height=72 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >将两个小动物融合，创造全新的生物。每一种独特组合都会生成一个全新物种，更有神秘的隐藏款等你来发现！同时，通过培育出独特的小生命，达成特殊条件也会帮助你解锁新的地图更加美丽独特的装饰物。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3064030/extras/fbec20800f85e894c5ef92d5fbcdfa9a.poster.avif?t=1768882111\" width=634 height=218 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3064030/extras/fbec20800f85e894c5ef92d5fbcdfa9a.webm?t=1768882111\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3064030/extras/fbec20800f85e894c5ef92d5fbcdfa9a.mp4?t=1768882111\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3064030/extras/27d4ae20860d6831984cc393617141c0.avif?t=1768882111\" width=616 height=72 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在这里，你可以做的远不止于收集生物！你可以通过完成任务、探索新区域或购买，解锁各种装饰物，自由布置你的专属小天地。无论是宁静的花园，还是充满奇幻色彩的游乐场，一切由你决定！小动物们也会在这里安家，陪伴你度过每一天。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3064030/extras/5cc4859195b04c99bbf53eb1c6fb9a09.poster.avif?t=1768882111\" width=758 height=218 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3064030/extras/5cc4859195b04c99bbf53eb1c6fb9a09.webm?t=1768882111\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3064030/extras/5cc4859195b04c99bbf53eb1c6fb9a09.mp4?t=1768882111\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >加入愿望单，一起开启冒险</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你好，我们是独立游戏开发者 Toadzillart 和 Tadpoly，神奇动物养殖中心是我们正在开发的第一款游戏。如果你对 神奇动物养殖中心 感兴趣，请考虑将它加入愿望单。这是支持我们创作旅程的最好方式。感谢你帮助我们将这个奇幻世界变为现实。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3064030/extras/3731df1a68d901bd36b149887d797926.apng?t=1768882111\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3064030/extras/3731df1a68d901bd36b149887d797926.poster.avif?t=1768882111\" class=\"bb_img\" width=192 height=192 /></picture></span></p>",
